nodes.text: Cyreno Taegon was a Human who worked as the Vice President of the Cularin Trade Alliance at around the time of the Clone Wars. After the company President Echari Di'San was arrested over the murder of Rysko Barnt, this threatened the company's reputation, so Taegon met with the Heroes of Cularin on Dorumaa and hired them to find out the truth about Barnt's death and prove that Di'San was innocent.
